      • setup

        public void setup(int propertyFileCode,

        Set-up the global attributes. If the attributes have not yet been set, this will get the attribute values from the properties file.
        Parameters:
        propertyFileCode - Property file code (either PropertyFileNames.KONAKART_SERVER_PROPERTIES_FILE or PropertyFileNames.KONAKARTADMIN_SERVER_PROPERTIES_FILE)
        defPropsFile - Default properties file for the current webapp (likely to be konakart.properties or konakartadmin.properties)
